io.netty5.handler.codec.compression.CompressionException

  • Packages that use CompressionException 
    Package Description
    io.netty5.handler.codec.compression
    Encoder and decoder which compresses and decompresses io.netty5.buffer.ByteBufs in a compression format such as zlib, gzip, and Snappy.
